Tilbake til 100 BC

Klarer du å løse dette super-avanserte chifferet?!

Kryptert: pgs{pnrfne_re_yvgg_tnzzryqntf}

(Bare små bokstaver)


---

Writeup
---

This is a simple Caesar-cipher with a rotation of 13-characters. This is easily noticed by the lack of encryption of the non-alphabetic characters ({ and _). The 13-char rotation can easily be found by trial-and-error/bruteforce.

Decrypting it yields:

ctf{caesar_er_litt_gammeldags}


